```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Page as PoliticianDetailsPage
    participant PPRC as PoliticianPositionRetrieveController
    participant API as API Server
    participant CS as CandidateStore

    Note over CS: Step 1: Page loads<br/>positionListRetrieveCompleteByBallotItem = {}<br/>Getter returns false for any candidate

    Note over CS: Step 2: Politician data arrives

    CS->>CS: candidateListsByPoliticianWeVoteId[adrianSmithId]<br/>= [{ we_vote_id: "wv02cand12345", ... }]
    CS->>CS: Emit change

    par PoliticianPositionRetrieveController
        CS-->>PPRC: onCandidateStoreChange()
        PPRC->>PPRC: Sees candidate list exists
        PPRC->>API: positionListForBallotItemPublic("wv02cand12345")
    and PoliticianDetailsPage (Step 3)
        CS-->>Page: onCandidateStoreChange()
        Page->>CS: getAllCachedPositionsByPoliticianWeVoteId()
        CS-->>Page: Returns []
        Page->>CS: positionListRetrieveHasCompletedForCandidate("wv02cand12345")
        CS-->>Page: Returns false
        Page->>Page: positionRetrieveCompleted = false
        Note over Page: Still loading → keep min-height ✓
    end

    Note over API: Step 4: API responds with count = 0

    API-->>CS: positionListForBallotItem { count: 0, ballot_item_we_vote_id: "wv02cand12345" }
    CS->>CS: positionListRetrieveCompleteByBallotItem["wv02cand12345"] = true
    CS->>CS: count === 0 → return updated state (with flag)
    CS->>CS: Emit change

    Note over Page: Step 5: Page re-reads store

    CS-->>Page: onCandidateStoreChange()
    Page->>CS: getAllCachedPositionsByPoliticianWeVoteId()
    CS-->>Page: Returns [] (still empty)
    Page->>CS: positionListRetrieveHasCompletedForCandidate("wv02cand12345")
    CS-->>Page: Returns true
    Page->>Page: positionRetrieveCompleted = true
    Note over Page: Confirmed empty → remove min-height ✓
